ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nilufer-Yanya-press-shot-Credit-Molly-Daniel-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nilufer-Yanya-press-shot-Credit-Molly-Daniel-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nilufer-Yanya-press-shot-Credit-Molly-Daniel-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nilufer-Yanya-press-shot-Credit-Molly-Daniel-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nilufer-yanya">Nilüfer Yanya</a>分享了她即将发行的专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nilufer-yanya-announces-new-album-my-method-actor-and-shares-new-single-3765867">My Method Actor</a> ”中的变革性新单曲“Mutations”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/nilufer-yanya-painless-review-3169953"><b>Nilüfer Yanya – 《Painless》评论：当她全力以赴时，受垃圾摇滚影响的专辑飙升</b></a></li></ul><p>《Mutations》以充满活力的贝斯和鼓声开场，以 Yanya 深沉而轻快的声音为中心，歌手唱道： <em>“旧的感觉/不要让他们进来/放手，保持那个愿景/挂断电话，我前往你的/谴责/等等，我正在前往你的/并发症/你的突变，</em> ”描述了微妙地改变和塑造了她的经历。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时，Yanya 分享道：“《Mutations》涉及环境带来的变化。这不是凤凰浴火重生，而是数以百万计的微小决定和行动塑造你的存在时不断发生的微妙变化。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nilüfer Yanya - 突变（官方可视化工具）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gLg7irPERfg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “对我来说，这有点像生存，”她继续说道。 “与其说是一种转变，不如说是一些从你的环境和周围环境中诞生的东西，你需要做这些事情才能生存。突变只是你必须经历的事情——你必须进化。”</p><p>这首歌的伴奏视觉效果由 Yanya 的妹妹 Molly Daniel 执导，展示了歌手在西班牙街道和海滩上行走的片段。</p><p> 《Mutations》是 Yanya 即将发行的专辑《My Method Actor》中分享的第四首单曲。继之前发行的《Call It Love》、《Like I Say (I Runaway)》和主打单曲《 <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nilufer-yanya-announces-new-album-my-method-actor-and-shares-new-single-3765867">Method Actor</a> 》之后。该密纹唱片定于 9 月 13 日通过 Ninja Tune 发行，可<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://niluferyanya.lnk.to/my-method-actorAI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预购/预保存</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8Cok5ftTyZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.11