祷”专辑的35周年</a>。限量版发布将于9月6日发布 -<a href="https://m.lnk.to/LAPSilver" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订包装</a>。</p><p>这张专辑的标志性标题曲目<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/marvel-officially-release-battle-royale-and-choir-remixes-of-madonnas-like-a-prayer-from-deadpool-wolverine-3782885">最近在Marvel的<i>Deadpool＆Wolverine</i>的配乐中包含</a>，现在在Streaming上提供了两个新的混音。</p><p>上个月还出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-reveals-biopic-whos-that-girl-is-back-in-the-works-is-rewriting-script-3775631">她一生的传记片回来</a>，麦当娜本人说她正在重写剧本，暂时命名<i>为那个女孩</i>。</p><p>这部电影已经推测了几年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-biopic-starring-julia-garner-scrapped-3386104">但据报道去年被报废</a>。</p><p>庞贝邮政官员在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pompeii-officials-respond-after-rumours-of-madonna-mega-birthday-party-spark-outrage-3783754">关于麦当娜“大型”生日派对Spark愤怒的谣言后的回应</a>。</p> ;
